| Lighthouse 85+ mobile | Measure in devtools; report score in live test | Note commitment to performance |
| Six-dimension scoring chart | Chart renders with labels, weights, interactivity | Screenshot in deck; explain the weighting logic |
| $75K funds breakdown | Graphic shows allocation summing to $75K | Screenshot; note accessibility (color-blind safe) |
| Org Hub wireframe mockup | Visual appears intentional and product-like | Screenshot; explain the feature |
| Email capture + CSV export | Form submits; email persists; /csv-export returns rows | Describe backend integration |
| Analytics setup | Plausible/Fathom events fire; console shows events | Mention privacy-respecting approach |
| WCAG 2.1 AA | No Lighthouse accessibility failures; pass keyboard nav test | Commit to accessibility standard |
| GoFundMe CTA | Button links to campaign or placeholder | Note it in deck |
| US-based developer | Note in cover letter | "I'm US-based and available..." |

